$ Simply-Supported Square Plate - Natural Frequencies
$ 4x4 CQUAD4 mesh, L=1.0m, t=0.01m, Steel
$ Analytical: f_mn = (pi/2)*sqrt(D/(rho*t)) * (m^2/a^2 + n^2/b^2)^0.5
$ D = E*t^3/(12*(1-nu^2)) = 2.1e11*0.01^3/(12*(1-0.09)) = 192.31 N*m
$ f_11 = (pi/2)*sqrt(192.31/(7850*0.01)) * sqrt(1+1) = 48.67 Hz (approx)
$
NASTRAN SYSTEM(1)=0
ID PLATE,MODES
SOL 103
